        <p>Hi, I'm Muhammad Abbas — a content writer specializing in SEO blog articles, informative long-form content, and product descriptions that don't just sit on a page — they do a job.</p>
        <p>I write for international brands across the health, business, lifestyle, and e-commerce niches. My process starts with understanding your audience: who they are, what they're searching for, and what moves them to act. Every piece I deliver is original, plagiarism-free, and optimized to perform in search.</p>
